title: GTA Online: Money Fronts
headline: GTA Online: Money Fronts
subtitle: New Hands On Car Wash Property
content:
The Hands On Car Wash in Strawberry is the perfect vintage facade to conceal your illegal activity and the heart of your new money laundering operation.

Pick up Martin Madrazoâ€™s call, meet him at LSIA, then head to the blip on the Map, the For Sale sign, or to Maze Bank Foreclosures to purchase the Hands On Car Wash.

Acquiring the Car Wash unlocks two more properties for purchase and a cash boost for Counterfeit Cash Factory Sell Missions.
